康达斯表示，自己拍摄《告密者》的目的是要把人口贩卖“昭告天下”：“没有任何人在向政府施压阻止这一切，没有任何人对此负责。这是懒惰造成的。”<ref name="Karpel" />

=== 拍摄 ===
《告密者》是一部[[加拿大|加拿大]]和[[德国|德国]]合拍的电影<ref name="Holden" />。薇兹于2007年从制片人艾米·考夫曼手中拿到剧本。由于正怀有身孕<ref name="Lacher" />，她起初谢绝了这个角色。但薇兹表示，这个故事一直困扰着自己<ref name="Zakarin" />，于是她之后主动联系了考夫曼，询问自己是否还能够加入<ref name="Zakarin" />，再于2009年8月签约出演<ref name="Trio">{{cite news | last = Siegel | first = Tatiana | archivedate = 2013-10-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131027190519/http://variety.com/2009/biz/news/trio-join-weisz-for-indie-whistleblower-1118010191/ | url = http://variety.com/2009/biz/news/trio-join-weisz-for-indie-whistleblower-1118010191/ | title = Trio join Weisz for indie 'Whistleblower' | work = Variety | date = 2009-08-20 | accessdate = 2014-08-16 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，电影则在2009年10月开拍<ref name="Blaga">{{cite news |last=Blaga |first=Lulia |title=Whistleblower begins filming at MediaPro Studios |work=Film News Europe |date=2009-10-28 |accessdate=2014-08-16 |archivedate=2013-10-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131018024454/http://www.filmneweurope.com/news/romania/3735-whistleblower-begins-filming-at-mediapro-studios/menu-id-159 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.filmneweurope.com/news/romania/3735-whistleblower-begins-filming-at-mediapro-studios/menu-id-159 }}</ref><ref name="Liao">{{cite news | last = Liao | first = Shannon | title = Blowing the Whistle on the U.N.'s Big Secret | work = The Epoch Times | date = 2011-08-05 | accessdate = 2014-08-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-17 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131017072125/http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/arts-entertainment/the-whistleblower-film-shines-light-on-the-uns-big-secret-60002.html | url = http://www.theepochtimes.com/n2/arts-entertainment/the-whistleblower-film-shines-light-on-the-uns-big-secret-60002.html }}</ref>。

电影大部分镜头都是在[[罗马尼亚|罗马尼亚]]的[[布加勒斯特|布加勒斯特]]取景，波克瓦克亲自到访了这里的拍摄片场<ref name="Zakarin">{{cite news | last = Zakarin | first = Jordan | title = Rachel Weisz In 'The Whistleblower': An Ordinary Woman Doing Extraordinary Things | work = The Huffington Post | date = 2011-10-01 | accessdate = 2014-08-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131022184904/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/08/01/rachel-weisz-in-the-whistleblower_n_914642.html | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2011/08/01/rachel-weisz-in-the-whistleblower_n_914642.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-10-22 }}</ref>。薇兹表示，为了准确诠释自己的角色，她只要头脑清醒时就会尽可能和波克瓦克待在一起<ref name="Lacher">{{cite news | last = Lacher | first = Irene | title = The Sunday Conversation: Rachel Weisz | work = Los Angeles Times | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jul/31/entertainment/la-ca-conversation-20110731 | date = 2011-07-31 | accessdate = 2014-08-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012194350/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jul/31/entertainment/la-ca-conversation-20110731 }}</ref>。薇兹和波克瓦克的外表明显不同，薇兹是黑发，体型苗条；而波克瓦克则是金发，远比薇兹要丰满和性感，并且身材上也要高大得多。在这样的情况下，女演员的工作重点就是模仿波克瓦克的口音和决心<ref name="Lacher" />。波克瓦克之后表示，由薇兹来扮演自己是很好的选择，还称赞她找到了正确的努力方向<ref name="PG">{{cite news |title=Q&A with Kathryn Bolkovac, inspiration for the film 'The Whistleblower' |work=Park & Go |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012010553/http://parkandgo.org/about/news/article/q/ |archivedate=2013-10-12 |url=http://parkandgo.org/about/news/article/q/ |accessdate=2014-08-16 }}</ref>。
