电影的拍摄工作持续了约6星期，这对[[惊悚片|惊悚片]]来说相对较短；薇兹表示，大部分惊悚片都需要拍上3个月才能完成<ref name="Rea">{{cite news | last = Rea | first = Steve | title = 'Whistleblower' Rachel Weisz haunted by Bosnian sex-slave story | work = The Post and Courier | url = http://www.postandcourier.com/article/20110828/ARCHIVES/308289907 | date = 2011-08-28 | accessdate = 2014-08-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131015015852/http://www.postandcourier.com/article/20110828/ARCHIVES/308289907 }}</ref>。制片人采用了手持式摄像机<ref>{{cite web | last = Whitman | first = Howard | title = Blu-ray Movie Review: The Whistleblower | url = http://www.technologytell.com/hometech/83587/blu-ray-movie-review-the-whistleblower/ | work = Technologytell | date = 2012-02-17 | accessdate = 2014-08-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131019112231/http://www.technologytell.com/hometech/83587/blu-ray-movie-review-the-whistleblower/ }}</ref>，拥有的拍摄预算在同类电影中也比较低<ref name="Rea" />。康达基表示，在[[东欧|东欧]]取景拍摄对这部电影来说至关重要：“对于这样一个故事来说，更重要的是你没有看见的东西，所以你必须要创建出那个世界”<ref name="Liao" />。罗马尼亚境内的[[喀尔巴阡山脉|喀尔巴阡山脉]]是片中20世纪末饱受战火蹂躏的[[塞拉耶佛|塞拉耶佛]]风景镜头的主要取景地<ref name="Liao" />。联合国大楼内部的镜头则是在[[多伦多|多伦多]]拍摄<ref name="Toumarkine">{{cite news | last = Toumarkine | first = Doris | title = Film Review: The Whistleblower | work = Film Journal | date = 2011-08-01 | accessdate = 2014-08-16 | archivedate = 2013-10-14 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131014093308/http://www.filmjournal.com/filmjournal/content_display/reviews/specialty-releases/e3ie15a1e0213bcf60f56e23ddbbde60ff8 | url = http://www.filmjournal.com/filmjournal/content_display/reviews/specialty-releases/e3ie15a1e0213bcf60f56e23ddbbde60ff8 }}</ref>。电影中的大部分户外镜头的时间都在夜间，白天的镜头经常表现得苍凉、灰白而阴暗，这些特点与镜头中的颗粒感相结合，有助于营造出一种[[纪录片|纪录片]]的风格<ref name="Baine">{{cite news | last = Baine | first = Wallace | title = 'Whistleblower' focuses on horrors of sex trafficking | work = Santa Cruz Sentinel | url = http://www.santacruzsentinel.com/ci_18705054 | date = 2011-08-18 | accessdate = 2014-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131017181537/http://www.santacruzsentinel.com/ci_18705054 | archive-date = 2013-10-17 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。
